{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2011}} Venezuela is one of the [[List of countries by oil production|world's largest producers of oil]], and the country with the [[List of countries by proven oil reserves|largest proven oil reserves in the world]]. Venezuela is a member of [[OPEC]].
Electricity in Venezuela is predominantly produced from [[hydroelectricity]].
